long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Save time with Autofill Factorial, the Chrome extension that fills your Factorial monthly work hours automatically. Set your schedule once, and let it do the rest!

Quick setup: Customize hours by day.
One-click autofill: Simplify repetitive tasks.
Secure: Your data stays private in your browser.
Boost your efficiency with Autofill Factorial!
